      "content": "makes sense. what about the counter-argument that the government has to regulate things to prevent actual harm, like hate speech or misinformation? how would someone using those philosophical frameworks respond to that? is there a way to argue that the \"harm\" caused by unregulated speech is actually less important than the principle of absolute free expression?",
